---
title: Japanese-Style Beef & Pork Stir-Fry with Jasmine Rice, Veggies & Sesame Mayo
description: Fragrant rice piled with stir-fried veggies and beef, could this be the new favourite dinner? When we season the beef
with a teriyaki sesame sauce mixture then it’s certainly a guarantee.
